5️⃣ Main Functions (isi form)

Isi ini (copy saja):

BeePetMart Middleware is an omnichannel integration platform designed to help e-commerce sellers manage their operations across multiple marketplaces.

The system integrates Lazada with ERP systems such as Odoo to synchronize products, inventory, prices, and orders automatically.

Main functions include:

• Product listing and catalog synchronization
• Real-time inventory updates
• Price management across marketplaces
• Order synchronization from Lazada to ERP
• Multi-channel marketplace management

This platform helps sellers automate marketplace operations and reduce manual work.

