The platform supports integration with multiple e-commerce platforms and ERP systems.

Supported marketplaces:
• Lazada
• Shopee
• Tokopedia
• TikTok Shop

Supported ERP systems:
• Odoo ERP
• Custom ERP systems via REST API

The middleware is designed to synchronize product catalog, inventory, pricing, and orders across all supported platforms.